1
00:00:11,541 --> 00:00:13,375
How many times do I have to tell you?

2
00:00:30,250 --> 00:00:31,250
I'm sorry.

3
00:00:34,916 --> 00:00:35,916
Don't be scared.

4
00:00:39,083 --> 00:00:40,208
Sorry.

5
00:00:43,291 --> 00:00:45,291
Why do you always make me do this?

6
00:00:45,375 --> 00:00:47,750
I can't handle it, and then…

7
00:00:49,416 --> 00:00:51,250
I don't want this either, all right?

8
00:00:56,375 --> 00:01:00,000
How many years? Seven years…

9
00:01:04,958 --> 00:01:07,125
Sorry, it's my fault.

10
00:01:19,166 --> 00:01:20,000
Jin Jin.

11
00:01:21,625 --> 00:01:23,375
I can't face her.

12
00:01:36,416 --> 00:01:37,750
Hi.

13
00:01:37,833 --> 00:01:40,791
Mom, what're you up to?
What took you so long to answer?

14
00:01:40,875 --> 00:01:43,166
Nothing, I was just busy.

15
00:01:43,250 --> 00:01:46,375
I'm at the hotel pool.
Let me show you the night view.

16
00:01:46,458 --> 00:01:47,958
It's stunning.

17
00:01:48,041 --> 00:01:49,291
I'm with An Chi.

18
00:01:49,833 --> 00:01:51,291
Hello, An Chi.

19
00:01:51,375 --> 00:01:52,583
Hello.

20
00:01:52,666 --> 00:01:54,916
You two be careful over there.

21
00:01:55,000 --> 00:01:57,500
Don't worry. We're not kids anymore.

22
00:01:57,583 --> 00:02:00,583
Mom, I've got to go.
I just called to let you know I'm fine.

23
00:02:00,666 --> 00:02:01,583
Okay.

24
00:02:01,666 --> 00:02:04,416
And I uploaded a new video on YouTube.

25
00:02:04,500 --> 00:02:05,916
Remember to hit like.

26
00:02:06,000 --> 00:02:07,125
Okay.

27
00:02:07,625 --> 00:02:09,041
I'm hanging up. Bye.

28
00:02:09,833 --> 00:02:11,791
-Bye bye.
-Bye bye.

29
00:02:33,416 --> 00:02:35,500
JIN JIN

30
00:02:46,916 --> 00:02:48,125
Come join us!

31
00:02:55,541 --> 00:02:57,458
Hsin-yi, are you coming or not?

32
00:02:57,541 --> 00:03:00,375
Just tell your mom
you're going to shoot videos with me.

33
00:03:00,458 --> 00:03:03,416
We can split the earnings
from videos and ads.

34
00:03:03,500 --> 00:03:05,916
You can have fun and get paid.
How cool is that?

35
00:03:30,541 --> 00:03:32,708
Mom, I want to go to Benkha.

36
00:03:33,666 --> 00:03:34,750
What for?

37
00:03:35,541 --> 00:03:37,291
Jin Jin is there already.

38
00:03:37,375 --> 00:03:39,166
She keeps asking me to join her.

39
00:03:40,791 --> 00:03:42,791
There's still time before school starts.

40
00:03:42,875 --> 00:03:44,000
I can go on vacation.

41
00:03:46,875 --> 00:03:50,500
And I can film some content with them
and make some money.

42
00:03:53,875 --> 00:03:55,875
I told you not to worry about money.

43
00:03:57,333 --> 00:03:58,208
I'll handle it.

44
00:03:58,666 --> 00:03:59,500
But…

45
00:04:07,125 --> 00:04:08,750
-Go back inside.
-Okay.

46
00:04:08,833 --> 00:04:09,833
I'll finish up here.

47
00:04:41,791 --> 00:04:46,166
SCAMMERS GO TO HELL

48
00:05:21,458 --> 00:05:22,541
Officer Li!

49
00:05:23,125 --> 00:05:26,791
PRESENT DAY, BENKHA

50
00:05:31,583 --> 00:05:33,083
You want me to steal a corpse?

51
00:05:34,125 --> 00:05:35,500
Mm.

52
00:05:40,083 --> 00:05:43,708
Please. You think too highly of me.
I can't pull that off.

53
00:05:44,958 --> 00:05:46,958
You can, Mr. Li.

54
00:05:47,041 --> 00:05:49,583
Everyone in Chinatown knows
you're the go-to-guy.

55
00:05:50,250 --> 00:05:53,333
You're handsome and kind-hearted.

56
00:05:53,916 --> 00:05:55,291
Help us out.

57
00:06:09,250 --> 00:06:10,750
If you can meet this price,

58
00:06:10,833 --> 00:06:11,708
I'll do it.

59
00:06:16,125 --> 00:06:17,791
That's way too much.

60
00:06:24,500 --> 00:06:25,583
No bargaining.

61
00:06:29,875 --> 00:06:31,541
Don't give me that look.

62
00:06:31,625 --> 00:06:33,750
Any idea how many people
I'll have to bribe?

63
00:06:33,833 --> 00:06:36,041
Most of that will go to the morgue.

64
00:06:36,125 --> 00:06:38,208
I'll barely have anything left.

65
00:06:38,791 --> 00:06:40,375
If you didn't look so desperate…

66
00:06:44,500 --> 00:06:46,708
Whatever.
You've got time to think it over.

67
00:06:47,791 --> 00:06:49,750
Wait, fine…

68
00:06:50,916 --> 00:06:52,208
We'll pay.

69
00:06:52,291 --> 00:06:53,375
We'll find the money.

70
00:06:53,875 --> 00:06:54,708
We will.

71
00:06:56,250 --> 00:06:57,083
Good.

72
00:06:58,458 --> 00:07:00,166
Come up with the money quickly.

73
00:07:00,625 --> 00:07:03,708
The body will be cremated in 72 hours.

74
00:07:04,500 --> 00:07:05,333
Okay?

75
00:07:06,250 --> 00:07:09,916
Don't you want to know why
we want to steal Chang Shih-kai's corpse?

76
00:07:10,000 --> 00:07:11,750
If I ask you, will you tell me?

77
00:07:12,333 --> 00:07:14,125
If we do, can you lower the price?

78
00:07:16,166 --> 00:07:17,041
What do you think?

79
00:07:18,541 --> 00:07:19,375
In any case,

80
00:07:20,625 --> 00:07:22,083
you pay the money

81
00:07:23,375 --> 00:07:24,666
and I'll do the job.

82
00:07:25,541 --> 00:07:27,458
All right, you can go now.

83
00:07:27,541 --> 00:07:28,541
See yourselves out.

84
00:07:30,916 --> 00:07:33,333
Get the money quick. Time's running out.

85
00:08:05,208 --> 00:08:06,041
Who is it?

86
00:08:07,625 --> 00:08:08,458
Hsiang.

87
00:08:09,041 --> 00:08:10,166
Stop coming here.

88
00:08:10,250 --> 00:08:12,458
-Sorry.
-Don't apologize to me.

89
00:08:12,541 --> 00:08:14,958
If you're really sorry,
tell them to pay up.

90
00:08:15,500 --> 00:08:16,958
I thought of you as a friend.

91
00:08:17,041 --> 00:08:20,458
So I listened to you
and bought that life insurance for my mom.

92
00:08:20,541 --> 00:08:23,875
Now my mother's in the ICU
and desperately needs the money!

93
00:08:23,958 --> 00:08:26,500
But your company won't pay out!

94
00:08:26,583 --> 00:08:27,833
I tried to get it back

95
00:08:27,916 --> 00:08:31,250
but they said it's an investment-based
policy and it's all gone!

96
00:08:31,333 --> 00:08:32,458
You know what you are?

97
00:08:32,541 --> 00:08:35,541
-You're a scammer!
-I'll make it up to you. Here's some…

98
00:08:35,625 --> 00:08:38,166
-No, I don't want it!
-Don't be so mean.

99
00:08:38,250 --> 00:08:40,666
-I'm suing your company!
-She has it hard too.

100
00:08:40,750 --> 00:08:42,750
Karma will get you!

101
00:08:43,333 --> 00:08:45,500
Chao Ching, ignore him.
He doesn't mean it.

102
00:08:45,583 --> 00:08:46,666
She scammed us.

103
00:08:46,750 --> 00:08:48,000
Don't say that.

104
00:08:48,416 --> 00:08:49,833
-It's not her fault.
-No?

105
00:08:49,916 --> 00:08:51,958
Karma will get her! Serves her right!

106
00:09:00,666 --> 00:09:02,291
Ching, there you are.

107
00:09:02,375 --> 00:09:03,208
Have a seat.

108
00:09:07,375 --> 00:09:09,208
Things must be tough for you lately.

109
00:09:10,333 --> 00:09:11,375
I'm fine.

110
00:09:11,458 --> 00:09:16,333
Why don't I transfer your clients
to Hsiao-chou for the time being?

111
00:09:17,500 --> 00:09:20,416
I found those clients.
Why should I give them to her?

112
00:09:20,500 --> 00:09:23,750
Precisely because
you worked so hard to get those clients.

113
00:09:23,833 --> 00:09:26,041
We should do our best to keep them.

114
00:09:26,541 --> 00:09:29,000
I'm worried
you're spreading yourself too thin,

115
00:09:29,083 --> 00:09:31,000
so I want Hsiao-chou to help you out.

116
00:09:33,000 --> 00:09:36,083
Without any clients,
how will I reach my sales target?

117
00:09:36,166 --> 00:09:39,333
Don't worry about that.
The company's taken it into account.

118
00:09:40,250 --> 00:09:42,833
With your family's situation, the lawsuit,

119
00:09:42,916 --> 00:09:44,875
and dealing with those pesky reporters,

120
00:09:44,958 --> 00:09:46,333
it must be hard to focus.

121
00:09:46,416 --> 00:09:49,000
So we've decided to transfer you
to General Affairs.

122
00:09:49,083 --> 00:09:50,750
This will reduce your workload.

123
00:09:50,833 --> 00:09:52,791
You're demoting me?

124
00:09:52,875 --> 00:09:55,166
How will I survive on that salary?

125
00:09:55,250 --> 00:09:56,250
Don't worry.

126
00:09:56,333 --> 00:09:59,125
Once this matter is over,
you can transfer right back.

127
00:09:59,208 --> 00:10:00,791
I need money now more than ever.

128
00:10:00,875 --> 00:10:03,541
And the company
needs sales more than ever.

129
00:10:06,625 --> 00:10:08,458
The company always needs sales.

130
00:10:12,416 --> 00:10:15,333
To reach my sales targets
these past few years,

131
00:10:15,416 --> 00:10:18,541
I sold insurance policies
to many of my friends and family.

132
00:10:18,625 --> 00:10:20,541
But the company refused to pay up.

133
00:10:21,416 --> 00:10:24,583
Now everyone calls me a scammer.

134
00:10:25,125 --> 00:10:26,791
I gave a lot to this company.

135
00:10:26,875 --> 00:10:29,083
Now I'm being transferred
to General Affairs?

136
00:10:38,833 --> 00:10:40,041
Ching,

137
00:10:40,125 --> 00:10:43,458
that all happened
before I joined the company,

138
00:10:43,541 --> 00:10:45,083
so I know nothing about it.

139
00:10:45,166 --> 00:10:49,458
Besides, all of our products
comply with legal regulations now.

140
00:10:49,541 --> 00:10:51,250
-Are you saying
-This--

141
00:10:51,333 --> 00:10:52,875
the old products were illegal?

142
00:10:52,958 --> 00:10:54,500
Don't take it out on me.

143
00:10:54,583 --> 00:10:56,416
The company decided to transfer you.

144
00:10:56,500 --> 00:10:58,416
It had nothing to do with me.

145
00:10:59,958 --> 00:11:02,666
To put it bluntly, you want me to resign.

146
00:11:03,875 --> 00:11:05,916
That's nonsense.

147
00:11:07,333 --> 00:11:10,041
Look at all
that's happening to you right now.

148
00:11:10,583 --> 00:11:13,000
It must be hard to focus on your job.

149
00:11:13,083 --> 00:11:16,583
And our company
has always been very accommodating.

150
00:11:18,000 --> 00:11:19,416
Think about it some more.

151
00:11:20,083 --> 00:11:21,875
Where will you find another company

152
00:11:22,500 --> 00:11:24,166
as good as this one?

153
00:11:25,166 --> 00:11:26,166
You know I'm right.

154
00:11:50,916 --> 00:11:51,916
What are you doing?

155
00:11:53,416 --> 00:11:55,875
The manager
asked me to sort your client files.

156
00:11:55,958 --> 00:11:57,208
Hsiao-chou.

157
00:11:57,291 --> 00:11:58,541
-Yes?
-Come here.

158
00:11:59,791 --> 00:12:00,833
Sorry.

159
00:12:06,541 --> 00:12:08,750
-Do it later.
-Didn't you tell Ching?

160
00:12:08,833 --> 00:12:09,791
It was so awkward.

161
00:12:30,208 --> 00:12:31,916
Did you just get back?

162
00:12:32,000 --> 00:12:33,125
Traffic was terrible.

163
00:12:34,250 --> 00:12:36,958
I was swamped with work.
No time to pick you up.

164
00:12:38,416 --> 00:12:40,958
You don't need to take me
to the airport tomorrow.

165
00:12:41,041 --> 00:12:43,291
I don't trust a caregiver with Jin Jin.

166
00:12:43,375 --> 00:12:45,791
I'll go and renew my visa.

167
00:12:45,875 --> 00:12:48,250
I'll just get a taxi
and head over from there.

168
00:12:48,333 --> 00:12:49,333
Oh, okay.

169
00:12:54,041 --> 00:12:55,541
I'll just drop my things off.

170
00:13:04,958 --> 00:13:06,833
Don't you ever clean?

171
00:13:06,916 --> 00:13:08,416
I've been pretty busy lately.

172
00:13:24,250 --> 00:13:25,500
-Hey.
-I'm gonna shower.

173
00:13:25,583 --> 00:13:26,750
I have a meeting later.

174
