195
00:18:10,250 --> 00:18:13,291
I'm Hsu Yung, from Super News.
I'm doing an exclusive on fraud…

196
00:18:22,041 --> 00:18:22,875
Hello?

197
00:18:23,666 --> 00:18:26,708
Is this Hsu Yung,
the reporter for Super News?

198
00:18:28,208 --> 00:18:29,291
It's Chao Ching.

199
00:18:30,166 --> 00:18:31,333
I'm back in Taiwan.

200
00:18:41,625 --> 00:18:42,958
Were you drinking again?

201
00:18:44,000 --> 00:18:45,416
Sentenced to death.

202
00:18:45,500 --> 00:18:47,791
I wonder
what'll happen to the civil damages.

203
00:18:48,583 --> 00:18:50,333
-I'm feeling down.
-Give me a hand.

204
00:18:51,708 --> 00:18:53,166
Come and give me a hand.

205
00:18:53,250 --> 00:18:54,083
Oh.

206
00:18:58,333 --> 00:18:59,250
-Like this?
-Yes.

207
00:18:59,333 --> 00:19:00,541
One, two, three.

208
00:19:00,625 --> 00:19:01,958
Hey.

209
00:19:02,041 --> 00:19:03,291
Sorry.

210
00:19:11,708 --> 00:19:15,041
Help me contact a medical flight.

211
00:19:15,125 --> 00:19:18,208
I'm going to send Jin Jin back to Taiwan
in a few months.

212
00:19:18,291 --> 00:19:20,875
No problem. I'll arrange it right away.

213
00:19:27,666 --> 00:19:30,708
You haven't given me
this month's living expenses yet.

214
00:19:33,666 --> 00:19:35,208
Can we talk about this?

215
00:19:36,166 --> 00:19:39,750
Jin Jin made a lot
from that sponsored content.

216
00:19:41,125 --> 00:19:43,791
I don't think I need to keep paying.

217
00:19:43,875 --> 00:19:46,750
-I have lots of expenses myself.
-What kind of expenses?

218
00:19:47,375 --> 00:19:49,125
I'm doing business with a friend.

219
00:19:50,416 --> 00:19:55,416
I take care of all our household expenses
in Taiwan, don't I?

220
00:19:55,958 --> 00:19:57,375
Don't I contribute enough?

221
00:20:04,083 --> 00:20:06,041
I'm heading back to Taiwan tomorrow.

222
00:20:06,708 --> 00:20:09,333
-When will you be back?
-We'll see.

223
00:20:09,416 --> 00:20:12,083
Doubt I'll be in Southeast Asia
for work anytime soon.

224
00:20:12,166 --> 00:20:13,791
So you're saying

225
00:20:14,958 --> 00:20:16,708
I won't be seeing you or any money?

226
00:20:17,958 --> 00:20:20,458
That's not what I said. Or what I meant.

227
00:20:21,333 --> 00:20:23,500
I knew you'd get upset.

228
00:20:23,958 --> 00:20:27,625
I think we should make plans
for the future.

229
00:20:27,708 --> 00:20:29,791
He's dead now.

230
00:20:29,875 --> 00:20:31,958
Just let things come to an end.

231
00:20:32,041 --> 00:20:34,416
We need to let go
and stop punishing ourselves.

232
00:20:34,500 --> 00:20:36,875
We should move on.

233
00:20:36,958 --> 00:20:38,916
I think we should move on too.

234
00:20:44,166 --> 00:20:45,166
That's right.

235
00:20:45,250 --> 00:20:48,750
So, can we discuss
what I mentioned last time?

236
00:20:48,833 --> 00:20:50,000
Sure.

237
00:20:50,875 --> 00:20:53,625
Good. I want to make things clear.

238
00:20:53,708 --> 00:20:56,666
-So if we separate in the future--
-Not in front of Jin Jin.

239
00:20:57,625 --> 00:20:59,541
Okay, not now.

240
00:21:00,083 --> 00:21:02,291
-I'll do it.
-No, I'll do it myself.

241
00:21:03,125 --> 00:21:05,166
Okay, then let's talk at my hotel.

242
00:21:08,041 --> 00:21:09,208
Hua Hsin!

243
00:21:09,291 --> 00:21:11,666
-Hua Hsin makes dirty money!
-You scammers!

244
00:21:11,750 --> 00:21:13,833
-Swindlers!
-Scammers!

245
00:21:13,916 --> 00:21:16,375
-You exploit people!
-Pay us back!

246
00:21:16,458 --> 00:21:18,208
-Hua Hsin, pay up!
-Scammers, pay up!

247
00:21:18,291 --> 00:21:21,500
-Hua Hsin, pay up!
-Hua Hsin, give us back our money!

248
00:21:21,583 --> 00:21:23,333
Pay us back!

249
00:21:23,416 --> 00:21:25,333
-Come out and face us!
-Scammers!

250
00:21:26,958 --> 00:21:29,166
-Scammers!
-Hua Hsin, pay us back!

251
00:21:31,333 --> 00:21:32,791
Ching, you have a guest.

252
00:21:35,375 --> 00:21:37,875
Yes, I know your show
is incredible at exposés.

253
00:21:37,958 --> 00:21:39,833
My business card. Hsu Yung, Super News.

254
00:21:39,916 --> 00:21:41,333
You can just call me Yung.

255
00:21:41,416 --> 00:21:43,666
To help Super News get the truth,
I go super.

256
00:21:45,458 --> 00:21:46,958
Ching, there you are.

257
00:21:47,458 --> 00:21:48,541
-Mr. Hsu.
-Ching.

258
00:21:48,625 --> 00:21:51,583
Congratulations.
Justice has finally been served.

259
00:21:53,666 --> 00:21:54,500
By the way,

260
00:21:54,583 --> 00:21:58,083
Mr. Hsu said you two
have something to discuss today.

261
